1.3
log
@From a syslog perspective it does not make sense to log fatal and
warn with the same severity.  Switch log_warn() to LOG_ERR and keep
fatal() at LOG_CRIT.
OK reyk@@ florian@@
@
text
@/*	$OpenBSD: log.c,v 1.2 2017/03/13 21:20:56 bluhm Exp $	*/

/*
